*rivendell-1.7.0-r1 (25 Apr 2010)

  25 Apr 2010; Emery Hemingway <emery@icmlf.net +rivendell-1.7.0-r1.ebuild:
  Set rivendell user and group UID to 585 to reduce permissions errors in
  networked systems. Changed /var/snd intial permissions. Moved rivendell
  CGI stuff to /usr/libexec/rd-bin.

